{"tid":953652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿同學失約　男生上門找晦氣激動送院","createTime":"2018-12-24T05:58:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T13:05:05.000Z","uid":30647,"like":514,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"68b0517c876d30c3d4cc391bc50381e5c7b8c145","tid":953652,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T05:58:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n油塘高翔苑高麟閣一單位，今早(24日)11時10分，一名10餘歲中學男生疑不滿男同學「放飛機」，失約未有現身，於是氣憤難平，登門往對方寓所找晦氣，並且大力拍打大門鐵閘。同學的胞姐見男生情緒激動，恐有事故發生，慌忙報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n警方及消防到場調查，好言安慰男事主後，由於他情緒不穩，需要由救護車送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181224/photo/bkn-20181224130154992-1224_00822_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181224%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181224130154992-1224_00822_001_01b.jpg&h=72182019&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181224/bkn-20181224130154992-1224_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181224%2Fbkn-20181224130154992-1224_00822_001.html&d=TQx6GH%2FuAz9pcikEHCQ2%2BDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=b41814b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181224/bkn-20181224130154992-1224_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f89f6b5ca9c0d570e3d494fe1b5718924e901fa3","tid":953652,"uid":7435,"like":546,"dislike":3,"score":543,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T05:59:34.000Z","msg":"新感冒童<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c07d0ccd1dff2abc776e9ff1ead5f0c915506eb9","tid":953652,"uid":146435,"like":314,"dislike":3,"score":311,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T06:00:11.000Z","msg":"平安夜棍搞下基 出下野都比人放飛機"},{"pid":"0d9d9b68479c5630eec1b9a218d3